claim.claim-text:
1. An electrostatic coating system, comprising: 
a disposable or recyclable intermediate interposed at a junction between an article to be coated and an electrically conductive hanger, wherein said intermediate is of pliable, electrically conductive material and serves to protect said hanger, thereby preserving its useful life, while simultaneously promoting coating of said article; 
the intermediate comprising a tubular member for engaging over a hanger.

29. An electrostatic coating system, comprising: 
a disposable or recyclable intermediate interposed at a junction between an article to be coated and an electrically conductive hanger, wherein said intermediate is of pliable, electrically conductive material and serves to protect said hanger, thereby preserving its useful life, while simultaneously promoting coating of said article; 
the intermediate comprising a strip of pliable, electroconductive material having an upper face and a lower face, and a layer of electrically conductive adhesive for securing the strip to an upper surface of the hanger.
